sentences: Eddie Lund (October 12, 1909 – December 4, 1973) was a pianist and bandleader.
He later moved to Tahiti in either 1936 or 1938 where he stayed permanently and published and released many records.
He picked up the Tahitian language quickly and secured a residence at Quinns night club in Papeete.
